{"tid":876842,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"品牌代言人被發現使用 iPhone X 俄國名嘴被***起訴","createTime":"2018-10-26T02:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T02:19:48.000Z","uid":71215,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8ef2e6b13778c1879478c02eab253e162448c6","tid":876842,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"品牌代言人被發現使用另一品牌的產品，很多時會引發公關災難。以往有不少為 Samsung 代言的明星名人，被發現手執 iPhone 拍照或發 Tweet，結果在網民一輪談論之後，通常都不了了之。不過最近發生的一宗同類事件，Samsung 卻選擇將之訴諸法院解決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1026-3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F1026-3a.jpg&h=c32ac2f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電視真人騷節目主持兼政客 Ksenia Sobchak 在俄羅斯是 Samsung 的品牌代言人，幾乎所有人一見到她就會聯想到 Samsung。她的代言人合約包括在公眾場合使用 Samsung 的智能手機，不過在早前的一個電視訪問中，儘管 Sobchak 嘗試以一張紙遮蓋，但鏡頭還是捕捉到她使用 iPhone X，而眼利的觀眾亦察覺到。<br />\n<br />\n有報導指 Sobchak 已非第一次被發現使用 iPhone，Samsung 俄羅斯亦有所行動，決定控告對方違約，並向她追討 1.08 億盧布（約 1,291 萬港元）違約賠償。<br />\n<br />\n來源：pocketnow<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nan***狗不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a9c12be58177cf0845712680061f4760f323e5","tid":876842,"uid":38173,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"抵撚死,  idog 就係咁無道德, 唔尊重合約精神, 眼中只有錢"},{"pid":"d90f8008981fc8f4b3489508498940815853bb5a","tid":876842,"uid":4790,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c0a9c12be58177cf0845712680061f4760f323e5","tid":876842,"uid":38173,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"抵撚死,  idog 就係咁無道德, 唔尊重合約精神, 眼中只有錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T02:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑大人個口"}]}